<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Turbocharger - Cleaning</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Cleaning</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Do not use a caustic solution on the turbocharger or its related components.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc graphiccount="0">
            <title>Turbocharger</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Use a suitable solvent and nylon brush to clean the turbocharger, pedestal, EBP control
                    valve (if equipped), charge air cooling tube/crossover pipe and hoses. Use filtered compressed air
                    to dry the parts.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Inspect the oil inlet and oil drain ports for restrictions. Clean as required.</para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
